{
  "stem": "10272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were not coming in a village, like I went to Tereblya.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There-- and when a Jew went on the street, the whole village was with their eyes like this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they probably were more anti-Jewish because of Jewish merchants.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were very-- at that time, they had the-- they had some, some kind of complaints against Jewish merchants.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this complaint was, was-- made, made sense.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because I happen to remember, when I used to help out my father in store-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he told me on a Thursday he needed help because Thursday was the market day-- for the market day.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all these-- in-- around the surrounding villages and, and-- came to shop and to sell some stuff-- and to shop.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At that time, they would stop and buy all kind of-- so they would buy, say, a pound of sugar or a pound of, of something else, rice.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we didn't have these packages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had to weigh it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So instead of weighing, to go faster, you would prepare, say, like, 20 or 30 bags.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then somebody would come and stand-- they were standing in line.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would just give them the, the bag of sugar and take the money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this will go faster.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I-- he would put me near the-- near the-- to weigh the sugar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you would have to put on one side a weight of, say, a pound, and on the other side, to put-- they pay for the bag, to open it, and start to pour in the sugar, right?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I would do it, looking how he's doing it, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then he would say, no, no, no, don't do it this way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why not?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says, look at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You don't put the bag slowly down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You drop it in order for the-- for the-- Scale.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--scale to move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This way, you don't have to put so much stuff inside-- when the scale is moving.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I did it this way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I told him, Abba, it's not fair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This way, you're giving for-- less than, than, than the guy's paying for it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He pays for one pound.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wants to get a pound of, of sugar, all right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when you do it this way, you make the scale moving, he wouldn't get exactly a pound.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, this is-- this is a gimmick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You don't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we start an argument about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would make me-- get out, you don't want to do it, then don't do it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I want to do it, but I want-- I want you to be fair, not to do it this way.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do it my way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, you do it my way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, he says, if I want to have the, the, the price of the bag-- I want to have it-- not only a profit on the rice-- he will teach me a lesson.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, when you come and your-- and your mother sends you for the-- for, for rice, you give money?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, who is paying for the rice when I give her-- rice for your mother in the kitchen?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have to get this from someone somewhere, he says.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The profit is-- the profit is, is, is OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I have to also to get paid for the bag, which I am giving this stuff inside, you know, and also for the rice which I consume.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So this-- the, the, the, the, the residents, the Ruthenians, the non-Jewish people who would come to shop, they would go home.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they would say that it's not a full pound that they bought.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they would get mad at the Jewish storekeepers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they would-- that's why they start cursing at them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's only a small thing, right?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But this, together with the-- with the priest in, in the church, when they go and he gives a sermon, and he mentions them that Jesus was killed by the Jews, they created a climate of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, Hitler is coming! they would cry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would scream at me, Hitler is coming, you dirty Jew!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You go to Palestine, not steal here in, in our-- in, in, in, in, in here steal from us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were considered foreigners there, even though my father and my mother, they lived there for generations and generations in this-- in this-- in this area.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they never considered us as full citizens, recognizing us as citizens over there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For me, the Holocaust actually began in 1938, when I was shut out of-- of the school, when they said, no more school due to the-- due to the mobilization.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
